VDR Plugin 'wetter' Revision History
------------------------------------

2005-01-10: Version 0.0.1

- Initial revision.


Version: 0.0.2

- 	Change some Color changes
- 	Now you can define your own Target Directory with the -D option
	for example ./vdr -P'wetter -D /tmp/wetter'  
	be sure you have write access to this directory
-	Add the "-S" Option to set the source of the SatDownload Script
